These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, tea
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
2. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
3. the person watching time-travel movies is the person drinking milk##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | milk  | tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel     | fantasy   |
| Sport         | volleyball | cricket |
| Transport     | boat | quad-bike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, spinach
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: drama, scientific
2 different pets are kept: pony, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, car
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching drama movies is the person driving the car##1
3. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | raspberry     | spinach |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | drama  |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | pony     |
| Transport     | boat   | car    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
