The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, freelancer
2 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left or right of the freelancer##3
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the freelancer##1
3. the person drinking milk is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | juice     | milk |
| Job         | freelancer | videographer    |
| Pet         | snake         | hedgehog        |
| Transport   | trike         | snowmobile    |

