.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, cauliflower
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, singing
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep
1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the fan of dubstep is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | cauliflower   | broccoli  |
| Hobby         | baking | singing     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | dubstep         |

