.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, musician
There are 2 different nationalities: nigerian, russian
2 different pets are kept: mouse, bird
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4
2. the russian is on the far left or far right##3
3. the musician is the nigerian##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | musician | doctor    |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | russian |
| Pet           | mouse         | bird    |
| Sport         | rugby    | rowing   |

